        "@value": "for substance stem:[\"X\"] in a mixture, quotient of mass stem:[m_\"X\"] (<<iso80000-4>>) of substance stem:[\"X\"] and volume stem:[V] (<<iso80000-3>>) of the mixture:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\ngamma_\"X\" = m_\"X\"//V\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
