        "@value": "for substance stem:[\"X\"] in a mixture, quotient of mass stem:[m_\"X\"] (<<iso80000-4>>) of substance stem:[\"X\"] and total mass stem:[m] of the mixture:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nw_\"X\" = m_\"X\"//m\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
