        "@value": "distance (<<iso80000-3>>) a magnetic field penetrates the plane surface of a semi-finite superconductor according to the expression:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nB(x) = B(0) \"exp\" ((-x)/(lambda_\"L\"))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[B] is magnetic flux density (<<iec80000-6>>) and stem:[x] is distance (<<iso80000-3>>) from the surface\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
