        "@value": "Airy function",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[\"Ai\"(z) = 1/3 sqrt(z) [\"I\"_(-1/3)(w) - \"I\"_(1/3)(w)\\]]\n\nstem:[\"Bi\"(z) = sqrt(z/3) [\"I\"_(-1/3)(w) + \"I\"_(1/3)(w)\\]]\n\nwhere stem:[w=2/3 z^(3//2)].\n\nEntire solution of stem:[y'' - zy=0]",
        "@language": "en"
      },
